## API Reference

### Auth (No token required)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | Register user |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login → JWT token |
| GET  | `/api/auth/me` | My profile (token required) |
| POST | `/api/auth/change-password` | Change password |

**Login response:**
```json
{ "token": "eyJ...", "role": "admin", "name": "Silasya Admin" }
```
Use `Authorization: Bearer <token>` on all protected routes.

---

### PUBLIC — Passport QR Scan (No auth)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/api/passport/:sgtin` | Full 7-layer DPP |
| GET | `/api/passport/:sgtin?view=regulator` | + chain integrity + regulatory check |
| GET | `/api/passport/:sgtin?view=brand` | + Scope 3 ESG data |
| GET | `/api/passport/:sgtin/audit-file` | Regulator JSON download |
| GET | `/api/passport/:sgtin/scan-count` | Scan analytics per product |

