## User Roles

| Role | Access |
|------|--------|
| `admin` | Full access to everything |
| `brand_partner` | Create/manage products, all layers, certificates |
| `artisan_manager` | Manage artisans, clusters, manufacturing records |
| `regulator` | Read-only access to all data |

