## Regulatory Markets Covered

| Market | Regulation | What we provide |
|--------|-----------|-----------------|
| 🇪🇺 EU | ESPR / DPP mandate + Green Claims Directive | Full 7-layer DPP, blockchain proof |
| 🇺🇸 US | UFLPA (Uyghur Forced Labor Prevention Act) | Farm-level traceability, GOTS certs |
| 🇬🇧 UK | Green Claims Code (CMA) | LCA-verified impact data, artisan wage proof |